OL,3,CPlaid Cymru to offer trainee teachers
OL,4,Cup to #30,000 to study and work in
OL,5,CWales
OL,7,FPlaid Cymru has announced a new
OL,8,Fstrategy to tackle what it calls a
OL,9,F"crisis" in Wales's education system,
OL,10,Fand has promised to offer trainee
OL,11,Fteachers up to #30,000 to study and
OL,12,Fwork in the country.
OL,14,FAny financial support would be
OL,15,Fcontingent on recipients remaining in
OL,16,Fa Welsh teaching post for a minimum of
OL,17,Ffive years following their
OL,18,Fprobationary period. Wales already
OL,19,Fprovides similar grants of #15,000 for
OL,20,Fthose teaching in specific subjects.
