OL,3,CPlaid Cymru to offer trainee teachers
OL,4,Cup to #30,000 to study and work in
OL,5,CWales
OL,7,FThe plans, revealed at the party's
OL,8,Fannual conference in Swansea, also
OL,9,Finclude a commitment to increase
OL,10,Fteacher pay to match that of England.
OL,12,FPlaid Cymru's leader, Rhun ap
OL,13,FIorwerth, told the conference
OL,14,Fyesterday that the party is ready to
OL,15,F"replace" Labour in leading the next
OL,16,FWelsh Government, with recent polls
OL,17,Fshowing a surge in support for Plaid
OL,18,FCymru. But this is closely following
OL,19,Fby growing support for Reform UK.
