OL,3,CPlaid Cymru to offer trainee teachers
OL,4,Cup to #30,000 to study and work in
OL,5,CWales
OL,7,FEducation spokesperson Cefin Campbell
OL,8,FMS unveiled the "new national
OL,9,Fmission," arguing that current
OL,10,Fperformance in literacy and numeracy
OL,11,Fis failing to help pupils reach their
OL,12,Ffull potential.
OL,14,FMr Campbell blamed the Labour
OL,15,Fgovernment, stating: "Under Labour's
OL,16,Fwatch, Wales is facing a crisis in
OL,17,Fteacher recruitment and retention." He
OL,18,Fpromised that a Plaid Cymru government
OL,19,Fwould "deliver a bold, practical, and
OL,20,Finclusive strategy to renew
OL,21,Feducational standards."
